A.Mb=new B.Z(A.Mu,["Discourse construal: collective-disorder circulation around {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publish ward-level incident timelines for {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 separate lawful assembly from disorder with verified arrest/charge data. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Convene community liaison with protest organisers and affected businesses on {subject}{topic_suffix} within 14 days. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Announce differentiated enforcement criteria for {subject}{topic_suffix} with a public compliance tracker. {flow_hook}","Publish granular protest incident data for {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 peaceful vs. disorder counts by ward.","Stand up independent community forums where grievance narratives on {subject} are recorded, not dismissed.","Pair enforcement updates on {subject} with named liaison officers and published response-time targets.","Review public-order messaging on {subject}{topic_suffix} for selective-condemnation bias (\u03c3).","Discourse construal: institutional framing compressing {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Issue a clause-by-clause public response to {subject}{topic_suffix}, citing evidence for each condemnation line. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Hold a press briefing allowing follow-up questions on {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 not pre-approved questions only. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Commit to a 30-day review of messaging on {subject}{topic_suffix} with an independent fact-check partner. {flow_hook}","Release timestamped evidence packets for each claim in {subject}{topic_suffix}.","Open a structured Q&A channel on {subject} for journalists and affected communities.","Audit institutional drag (I\u03c4) where {resistance_snip} slows corrective response.","Differentiate peaceful civic expression from criminal acts in all {subject} communications.","Discourse construal: macro-economic and labour-pressure circulation on {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publish cost-impact tables for {subject}{topic_suffix} showing who bears disruption vs. relief. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Broker a timed negotiation on {subject}{topic_suffix} with unions, employers, and rider/user groups. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Announce phased reopening or relief steps for {subject}{topic_suffix} with measurable milestones. {flow_hook}","Publish daily disruption metrics for {subject}{topic_suffix} with cost borne by households and firms.","Convene a tri-party table on {subject} \u2014 labour, management, and service users \u2014 with published minutes.","Address stated resistance: {resistance_snip}","Preserve nuance in rider/user messaging: {flow_snip}","Discourse construal: electoral vortex polarising {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Release a voter-facing fact sheet on {subject}{topic_suffix} separating campaign claims from verified records. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Host a neutral-format public forum on {subject}{topic_suffix} with equal time for competing narratives. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Publish audit-ready timelines for {subject}{topic_suffix} decisions before voting windows close. {flow_hook}","Publish claim-vs-record matrices for {subject}{topic_suffix} with source links.","Fund neutral civic-information sessions on {subject} in high-shear districts.","Reduce institutional drag on electoral transparency for {subject}.","Track trust-transport (J\u03bc) gaps across voter segments on {subject}.","Discourse construal: narrative-lens compression on trust around {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Acknowledge where {subject}{topic_suffix} framing compressed nuance \u2014 publish a corrective narrative map. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Invite critics of {subject}{topic_suffix} to a structured evidence exchange, not a single podium. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Deploy differentiated outreach on {subject}{topic_suffix} for groups whose trust transport diverges. {flow_hook}","Map two-tier perception gaps on {subject}{topic_suffix} with quoted community sources.","Replace blanket condemnation lines on {subject} with event-level differentiation.","Address institutional scepticism: {resistance_snip}","Strengthen differentiated messaging: {flow_snip}","Discourse construal: accountability pressure on {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Hold an open press briefing on {subject}{topic_suffix} with published decision criteria and timelines. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Commission an independent summary of institutional process around {subject}{topic_suffix}. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Set binding review dates for {subject}{topic_suffix} with public progress markers. {flow_hook}","Publish decision criteria and timelines for {subject}{topic_suffix} before speculation hardens.","Independent process review for {subject} \u2014 scope, witnesses, and publication date fixed.","Reduce procedural drag where {resistance_snip}","Maintain transparent status updates on {subject} through the review window.","Discourse construal: open-ended \u03c9 scenario on {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Convene a scenario-specific public session on {subject}{topic_suffix} anchored to the stated \u03c9 question. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Map stakeholder positions on {subject}{topic_suffix} from the supplied \u03c3/I\u03c4 inputs. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Publish time-bound next steps on {subject}{topic_suffix} reflecting stated J\u03bc nuance. {flow_hook}","Ground public updates on {subject}{topic_suffix} in the user-stated \u03c9 question: {vortex_snip}","Address shear bias where stated: {shear_snip}","Work through institutional resistance: {resistance_snip}","Preserve trust-transport nuance: {flow_snip}","{agent}: Convene a public progress review on {subject}{topic_suffix} to sustain covariant continuity. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Publish constructive milestones on {subject}{topic_suffix} with community co-design. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Reinforce differentiated trust transport on {subject}{topic_suffix} across stakeholder groups. {flow_hook}","Sustain progressive momentum on {subject}{topic_suffix} with published cohesion indicators.","Co-design outreach on {subject} with groups where J\u03bc transport is strongest.","Reduce residual friction: {resistance_snip}","Amplify stated nuance: {flow_snip}"],t.w)
